name: Faith LastName
description:
Faith is the sixth member of the LastName family, for anyone who wants a consistent character for their SD 1.5 renders.

Faith is almost certainly out of your league. She's a musician and gymnast, who dreams of running away to join Cirque du Soleil (and almost certainly will). She was born during golden hour. She’ll take you camping on the beach, then wear a leather jacket over a loose-fitting top and somehow make it impossibly cool. As I said: she is almost certainly out of your league.

To use this embedding with the Automatic1111 web UI, save the downloaded file to /embeddings/faithlastnamesd15.pt, and then include the trigger word faithlastnamesd15 in your prompt. (All of the sample images have full prompt metadata, and are straight out of Standard Diffusion  - no upscaling, inpainting, or img2img was used.)
